# üîê SSH Setup

This folder contains notes and configuration examples for setting up SSH key-based access from a Windows PC to my Linux Mint home server.

## Summary

- SSH key pair generated on Windows
- Public key added to `~/.ssh/authorized_keys` on Linux and Windows
- Password login and root login disabled in `sshd_config`
- Windows `.ssh/config` used to simplify login

## Example SSH Config

```bash
Host homeserver
    HostName 192.168.x.xxx
    User <linux-user>
    IdentityFile C:/Users/<windows-user>/.ssh/LinuxHomeServerKey
